cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) because it deals with machine reading and text segmentation. It could also belong to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) because it deals with finding relevant information in documents. The use of deep neural networks suggests it could also belong to Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the focus on improving performance through evaluation and comparison of different architectures suggests it could also belong to Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
